WEBVTT

01:37.880 --> 01:41.039
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.950
[Episode 28]

01:47.310 --> 01:48.470
Over there.

01:49.350 --> 01:50.610
Be careful. Slow down.

01:51.950 --> 01:53.350
Come on. Close your eyes.

01:56.800 --> 01:57.500
Done.

01:57.620 --> 01:58.370
Thank you.

02:14.040 --> 02:15.840
Take a look at today's schedule.

02:16.230 --> 02:17.030
It's all here.

02:22.990 --> 02:23.920
Keep an eye on it.

02:24.520 --> 02:25.030
Got it.

02:27.120 --> 02:27.520
Okay.

02:30.300 --> 02:32.630
Mr. Xiao, you need to
keep an eye out later.

02:33.470 --> 02:34.360
When Zhichun talks about

02:34.360 --> 02:35.680
this year's college entrance exam,

02:35.680 --> 02:36.400
I'll give you a signal.

02:36.400 --> 02:37.800
Then, you can go on stage.

02:37.800 --> 02:38.150
Okay.

02:40.750 --> 02:41.280
Miyu.

02:42.870 --> 02:44.000
Your time to go on stage

02:44.000 --> 02:45.190
might not be fixed.

02:45.210 --> 02:47.570
It mainly depends on Kuanli's sales.

02:47.680 --> 02:50.110
The host might cue you to
go on stage at any time.

02:50.110 --> 02:52.170
Let me know if there are any problems.

02:52.360 --> 02:53.000
Thank you.

03:00.630 --> 03:02.140
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

03:09.560 --> 03:10.240
How is it?

03:10.260 --> 03:11.390
It's starting.

03:11.910 --> 03:12.360
Hello, everyone.

03:12.360 --> 03:13.900
Hello to everyone.

03:13.960 --> 03:15.750
Welcome to my live stream channel.

03:15.750 --> 03:18.280
I wonder if there are any

03:18.280 --> 03:20.440
college entrance exam-takers
watching my live stream right now.

03:20.440 --> 03:23.079
There's only half a month left
until the college entrance exam.

03:23.079 --> 03:23.750
I don't know

03:23.750 --> 03:25.560
if every family with
a college entrance exam-taker

03:25.560 --> 03:27.720
is giving it their all for a final push.

03:28.560 --> 03:29.590
Considering that it's a critical moment

03:29.590 --> 03:32.490
for exam-takers,

03:32.560 --> 03:33.750
we want to provide

03:33.750 --> 03:35.280
convenience in terms of your travel.

03:35.280 --> 03:37.190
In the following time,
the product in our live stream

03:37.190 --> 03:38.270
will be special.

03:38.400 --> 03:40.030
We have achieved a strategic cooperation

03:40.030 --> 03:41.910
targeting the newly added exam site

03:41.910 --> 03:43.870
this year

03:43.910 --> 03:45.079
with nearby five-star hotels

03:45.079 --> 03:47.440
for accommodation and dining.

03:47.590 --> 03:49.400
We hope that we,
who have been through it,

03:49.400 --> 03:51.120
can provide

03:51.120 --> 03:52.710
students who are about to take the exam

03:52.710 --> 03:55.310
with a high-end service
during the exam period.

03:55.310 --> 03:56.970
The first one is Kuanli Hotel.

03:59.710 --> 04:00.120
Hello.

04:00.180 --> 04:00.720
Hello.

04:00.910 --> 04:01.430
Please have a seat.

04:01.430 --> 04:01.800
Okay.

04:04.310 --> 04:05.710
The one who is sitting next to me is

04:05.710 --> 04:08.840
Mr. Xiao from the Marketing Department of
Kuanli Hotel.

04:09.400 --> 04:10.680
Let me introduce

04:10.980 --> 04:12.410
Kuanli Hotel.

04:12.870 --> 04:13.950
I guess everyone has heard of

04:13.050 --> 04:14.280
[Is this price real]

04:13.980 --> 04:15.480
Kuanli.

04:14.300 --> 04:15.330
[Well, staying at Kuanli costs too much]

04:16.430 --> 04:18.040
It is the best domestic hotel brand

04:18.040 --> 04:21.170
as well as the leader of
domestic high-end hotel chains.

04:21.360 --> 04:23.380
This guy talked even more arrogantly
than I do.

04:23.380 --> 04:23.980
By the way,

04:24.430 --> 04:26.330
ask

04:26.390 --> 04:28.450
who the representative of Purong is.

04:28.600 --> 04:31.220
I heard that Lu Zhenzhen
went to have a baby.

04:31.830 --> 04:34.510
Who could Ji Feng find to replace her?

04:35.360 --> 04:37.550
Xu Miyu, the Front Office's lobby manager.

04:37.550 --> 04:39.480
Since our live stream has just started,

04:39.480 --> 04:41.470
let's put up ten orders to warm up.

04:42.270 --> 04:43.310
Three, two, one,

04:43.330 --> 04:44.260
link in the chat!

04:45.430 --> 04:47.560
The area of Kuanli's standard double room

04:47.560 --> 04:48.830
is 35 square meters.

04:49.240 --> 04:50.900
What? All gone?

04:51.150 --> 04:51.870
Sorry.

04:51.870 --> 04:54.530
I haven't finished
introducing the product yet.

04:54.530 --> 04:55.430
It proves that everyone

04:55.430 --> 04:57.370
knows Kuanli Hotel very well.

04:57.430 --> 04:59.070
After all, it's a well-known hotel.

04:59.070 --> 05:01.120
Let's do ten more orders?

05:02.360 --> 05:02.750
Okay.

05:02.920 --> 05:04.430
Okay, let's put up ten more orders.

05:04.300 --> 05:05.600
[Kuanli is doing a promotion]

05:04.480 --> 05:05.410
Link in the chat!

05:05.630 --> 05:06.840
[The supply is limited]

05:06.630 --> 05:07.210
Mr. Xiao.

05:07.430 --> 05:09.830
Some followers just asked

05:09.870 --> 05:11.630
if there are
any catering services included.

05:11.630 --> 05:13.830
Well, we need to ask Mr. Xiao about this.

05:13.870 --> 05:15.750
You still have to go to our restaurant

05:15.750 --> 05:17.070
for regular consumption.

05:17.070 --> 05:18.630
Kuanli's discount

05:18.680 --> 05:20.800
is mainly on the accommodation.

05:21.270 --> 05:22.220
Sold out again?

05:21.340 --> 05:21.640
[My child is taking the exam at
Xinhua Finance and Economics School]

05:21.670 --> 05:22.240
[This is the biggest discount ever,
right]

05:22.510 --> 05:24.190
Everyone is really so enthusiastic.

05:24.190 --> 05:24.830
Mr. Xiao,

05:24.870 --> 05:26.430
do we still have rooms available?

05:26.430 --> 05:27.630
The last five orders?

05:28.190 --> 05:30.040
Director Zhao, are you kidding me?

05:30.040 --> 05:32.240
You promised to give me plenty of rooms.

05:32.680 --> 05:33.680
Mr. Duan Jr.,

05:34.190 --> 05:36.010
we only have 25 rooms left,

05:36.159 --> 05:37.560
and I gave them all to you.

05:37.870 --> 05:39.630
Kuanli has 460 rooms in total.

05:39.630 --> 05:40.530
You only gave me 25 rooms?

05:40.530 --> 05:41.500
Are you kidding?

05:41.630 --> 05:42.950
Thank you very much, Mr. Xiao,

05:42.950 --> 05:44.330
for coming to our live stream room.

05:44.330 --> 05:45.070
Cut the crap.

05:45.530 --> 05:46.530
I need another hundred rooms.

05:46.530 --> 05:48.120
Followers, don't be anxious.

05:48.120 --> 05:49.780
-Don't leave our live stream room.
-Miyu.

05:49.780 --> 05:51.600
-If you didn't get rooms in Kuanli,
-Get ready, please.

05:51.600 --> 05:52.800
it doesn't matter.

05:52.800 --> 05:53.720
Because next,

05:53.720 --> 05:54.600
what we are going to introduce is

05:54.600 --> 05:57.360
the promotion targeting
the college entrance exam

05:57.360 --> 05:59.800
of Purong Hotel, which enjoys
the same reputation as Kuanli.

05:59.800 --> 06:01.240
Let's welcome

06:01.240 --> 06:02.840
the lobby manager of Purong Hotel,

06:01.330 --> 06:02.030
[I don't think I can get a room]

06:02.050 --> 06:03.070
[It's still expensive
even though it gives discounts]

06:02.950 --> 06:03.750
Xu Miyu.

06:05.770 --> 06:06.800
Do you trust me?

06:09.160 --> 06:11.540
Last night at the Kuanli Hotel entrance,

06:11.830 --> 06:13.380
I saw Francis,

06:13.480 --> 06:15.360
the designated chef of

06:15.390 --> 06:16.370
the Global Internet and
Venture Capital Summit.

06:16.370 --> 06:19.450
His appearance there is an indicator.

06:19.560 --> 06:20.630
There's a high probability

06:20.630 --> 06:22.970
the Summit will be held at Kuanli again
this year.

06:22.970 --> 06:23.770
You know,

06:24.040 --> 06:25.390
the number of attendees

06:25.410 --> 06:26.810
is nearly 400 every year,

06:26.920 --> 06:28.520
which means at that time,

06:28.650 --> 06:30.910
Kuanli will definitely be fully booked.

06:32.390 --> 06:33.159
Are you sure?

06:34.630 --> 06:36.310
You can ask your friends about it.

06:36.310 --> 06:37.890
It's not a secret project.

06:37.990 --> 06:38.630
Moreover,

06:39.240 --> 06:40.040
this year's summit

06:40.040 --> 06:42.040
will be held earlier, in early June.

06:42.220 --> 06:44.870
It will coincide with
the college entrance exam.

06:44.870 --> 06:47.050
So, no matter
whose products are promoted first,

06:47.050 --> 06:49.380
Kuanli definitely won't make this money.

06:49.720 --> 06:51.680
So, you were prepared in advance?

06:54.690 --> 06:57.350
Hotel workers never go into battle
unprepared.

07:02.970 --> 07:03.710
Welcome. Welcome.

07:03.710 --> 07:04.340
Thank you.

07:04.750 --> 07:05.810
Please have a seat.

07:06.690 --> 07:07.560
So next,

07:07.560 --> 07:08.950
let's invite Ms. Xu

07:08.970 --> 07:10.040
to introduce

07:10.040 --> 07:12.300
the rooms in Purong Hotel for examinees.

07:13.120 --> 07:13.860
Okay.

07:14.390 --> 07:16.210
Thank you, Ms. Dianjiangchun.

07:16.800 --> 07:18.690
[Huge discounts]

07:17.560 --> 07:18.560
Hello, everyone.

07:18.560 --> 07:20.920
I am Xu Miyu,
the lobby manager of Purong Hotel.

07:18.710 --> 07:20.800
[My cousin needs it]

07:21.070 --> 07:22.920
This time, Purong Hotel

07:23.000 --> 07:23.950
will provide rooms on the upper floors,

07:23.950 --> 07:25.660
from the 12th to the 17th,

07:25.820 --> 07:28.040
exclusively for
college entrance exam-takers

07:28.040 --> 07:30.090
from June 6 to 10.

07:30.190 --> 07:31.430
There are two reasons.

07:31.430 --> 07:33.840
First, the upper floors are quiet.

07:33.920 --> 07:35.690
Second, we think

07:35.720 --> 07:38.159
concentrating these rooms

07:38.159 --> 07:39.270
can provide everyone with a

07:39.270 --> 07:40.720
better review atmosphere.

07:40.720 --> 07:41.670
Think about it.

07:41.720 --> 07:43.390
If your next-door neighbor

07:43.409 --> 07:44.620
and the neighbor next to them

07:44.620 --> 07:46.050
are all reviewing for the exam,

07:46.050 --> 07:46.920
wouldn't it feel like

07:46.920 --> 07:49.409
studying at school?

07:49.600 --> 07:50.600
Awsome!

07:50.720 --> 07:51.480
Everyone,

07:51.480 --> 07:52.850
listen carefully.

07:52.950 --> 07:54.560
Purong Hotel is offering

07:54.560 --> 07:57.040
entire floors of rooms for you.

07:57.270 --> 07:58.340
Let's imagine.

07:58.390 --> 08:01.000
It's like living in a school dorm.

08:01.070 --> 08:01.630
Everyone around is

08:01.630 --> 08:03.920
exam-takers preparing for the exam.

08:04.000 --> 08:05.530
The atmosphere is awesome!

08:06.360 --> 08:06.830
Yes.

08:07.900 --> 08:09.580
[Best rooms for
college entrance exam candidates ever]

08:09.160 --> 08:11.390
I noticed
someone is asking

08:09.600 --> 08:11.260
[Want to eat Yan Du Xian]

08:11.750 --> 08:13.360
about the food.

08:13.380 --> 08:14.260
Let me explain it.

08:13.910 --> 08:15.180
[I'll try to book Purong's room]

08:14.290 --> 08:17.030
We will prepare set meals for you.

08:15.210 --> 08:16.510
[Purong has a bigger discount
than a Kuanli]

08:17.170 --> 08:19.720
The menu will be updated
on our official website

08:19.720 --> 08:20.920
in the near future.

08:20.950 --> 08:22.290
During the exam period, we will

08:22.290 --> 08:24.690
provide exam-takers with a wide variety of

08:24.720 --> 08:27.370
tasty and nutritious set meals.

08:27.560 --> 08:30.000
The cost of the set meals

08:30.000 --> 08:32.620
is included in the total price.

08:33.480 --> 08:35.690
This is also a way for Purong Hotel

08:35.750 --> 08:38.140
to support and encourage the examinees.

08:38.120 --> 08:39.190
[Moms are eager to grab rooms]

08:38.240 --> 08:39.360
Someone is asking

08:39.210 --> 08:40.460
[Comparing to Kuanli, Purong provides
a bigger discount]

08:39.440 --> 08:41.870
if the set meals include
Yan Du Xian and boat pastries.

08:41.870 --> 08:43.750
Yes, they are included

08:43.750 --> 08:45.200
in our set meals.

08:45.330 --> 08:46.150
At the same time,

08:46.150 --> 08:49.070
we will serve breakfast
half an hour earlier than usual

08:49.070 --> 08:51.550
to give the examinees
plenty of time to eat.

08:51.580 --> 08:52.840
And after dinner,

08:52.840 --> 08:54.620
we will add a supper,

08:54.670 --> 08:57.570
so that students reviewing at night

08:57.630 --> 08:59.800
can also enjoy the meal service.

08:59.840 --> 09:01.750
We can also deliver meals

09:01.750 --> 09:03.680
directly to the examinees' rooms.

09:04.630 --> 09:06.100
The 100 orders are sold out.

09:05.250 --> 09:06.810
[My Internet connection is poor.
Can I make an offline reservation]

09:06.530 --> 09:07.220
Gosh.

09:06.830 --> 09:08.470
[Sold out in such a short time]

09:07.240 --> 09:08.640
We are going to set a record today.

09:08.640 --> 09:10.040
Let's add 50 more orders.

09:10.470 --> 09:11.160
No problem.

09:11.240 --> 09:12.270
Three, two, one.

09:12.290 --> 09:13.150
Link in the chat!

09:12.360 --> 09:13.020
[It's time to
put my reflexes to the test]

09:13.040 --> 09:13.830
[I'm ready]

09:13.900 --> 09:16.380
Ms. Xu, look, someone is asking,

09:16.410 --> 09:17.760
"The discount is huge,

09:17.530 --> 09:18.630
[I will feel sorry for the room
if my kid doesn't do well in the exam]

09:17.840 --> 09:19.360
if I'm not an examinee,

09:18.660 --> 09:19.370
[Non-exam-takers envy you a lot]

09:19.360 --> 09:20.370
can I still book a room?"

09:19.390 --> 09:20.020
[Can I enjoy the discount as well]

09:20.420 --> 09:21.380
I'm sorry.

09:21.510 --> 09:23.800
I have to disappoint this friend.

09:24.080 --> 09:26.150
Purong Hotel

09:26.180 --> 09:28.000
is dedicated to creating
the best learning environment for students

09:28.000 --> 09:30.690
during the college entrance exam period.

09:30.900 --> 09:33.200
This is

09:33.200 --> 09:34.470
our priority.

09:34.510 --> 09:36.240
So, we won't violate
our prioritized principle

09:36.240 --> 09:38.080
for our performance.

09:38.400 --> 09:40.630
At the same time, we will also strengthen

09:40.630 --> 09:43.630
security measures during this period.

09:43.670 --> 09:45.360
For example, upon check-in,

09:45.360 --> 09:46.870
we will check and register

09:46.870 --> 09:48.700
your admission ticket number.

09:48.790 --> 09:50.330
During the stay,

09:50.360 --> 09:52.900
we will arrange special security guards

09:53.120 --> 09:55.150
to irregularly patrol and inspect

09:55.270 --> 09:57.970
each floor

09:58.040 --> 09:59.700
to ensure everyone's safety.

10:00.120 --> 10:01.110
Sold out.

10:01.630 --> 10:02.440
Sold out.

10:02.750 --> 10:04.060
So fast!

10:04.200 --> 10:05.200
This tells us that

10:05.200 --> 10:07.460
in this seemingly saturated
commodity market,

10:07.460 --> 10:08.870
there are still many

10:08.870 --> 10:10.330
unseen demands.

10:10.720 --> 10:12.020
First of all, we should also thank

10:12.020 --> 10:13.930
these two leading hotels

10:13.970 --> 10:15.240
for noticing the needs of the examinees

10:15.240 --> 10:17.510
with such keen insight.

10:17.530 --> 10:18.790
Someone is asking that

10:19.150 --> 10:20.720
why you just provided a few rooms.

10:20.720 --> 10:22.470
Can you provide more rooms?

10:22.550 --> 10:24.480
Some also said their Internet is
too slow

10:24.480 --> 10:25.580
so they failed to book a room.

10:25.580 --> 10:26.260
[What a pity! I didn't get it]

10:25.870 --> 10:26.790
There are still 20 minutes left.

10:26.280 --> 10:26.970
[Is there any spare room]

10:28.080 --> 10:29.070
I'm sorry.

10:29.150 --> 10:31.030
We still have

10:31.030 --> 10:32.390
20 minutes left,

10:32.470 --> 10:34.500
but our stock is already gone.

10:38.760 --> 10:40.220
We can provide more rooms.

10:41.390 --> 10:42.120
How many?

10:42.550 --> 10:43.550
A hundred orders.

10:44.710 --> 10:45.870
Add another hundred orders!

10:45.870 --> 10:47.090
Three, two, one.

10:47.120 --> 10:48.050
Link in the chat!

10:48.540 --> 10:49.630
Add another hundred orders!

10:49.630 --> 10:50.720
Three, two, one.

10:50.740 --> 10:51.670
Link in the chat!

10:54.510 --> 10:55.240
Cut the crap.

10:55.720 --> 10:57.380
I want another hundred rooms.

10:57.720 --> 10:59.310
It's impossible, Mr. Duan Jr.

10:59.310 --> 11:01.240
Please don't make this hard for me.

11:02.760 --> 11:04.320
Parents and students

11:04.340 --> 11:05.720
who haven't ordered yet,

11:05.720 --> 11:08.250
-you need to seize the last chance.
-Get lost!

11:08.700 --> 11:10.410
I also want to ask Ms. Xu.

11:16.070 --> 11:18.460
Is Purong Hotel offering all of its rooms

11:18.490 --> 11:19.630
for examinees?

11:19.910 --> 11:20.940
Here,

11:21.360 --> 11:24.630
on behalf of Purong Hotel, I promise

11:24.790 --> 11:27.480
that during the exam period,
all our rooms will be reserved exclusively

11:27.480 --> 11:29.500
for exam-takers.

11:29.520 --> 11:32.390
Even if there are empty rooms, they
won't be used for other purposes.

11:32.390 --> 11:33.120
Excellent!

11:55.750 --> 11:57.150
What are you looking for?

11:57.480 --> 11:58.050
Where are the car key?

11:58.050 --> 11:58.710
Where is it?

11:58.870 --> 11:59.390
Here.

12:03.030 --> 12:05.110
Thank you. Okay.

12:24.330 --> 12:25.440
Where are you going?

12:25.440 --> 12:26.500
To pick someone up.

12:32.840 --> 12:35.200
That's wonderful. This is
probably the first hotel in the country

12:35.200 --> 12:37.600
that exclusively serves families
with college entrance exam candidates.

12:37.600 --> 12:39.740
I'm touched by your sincerity.

12:40.490 --> 12:42.770
Since families with
college entrance exam-takers

12:42.770 --> 12:44.140
count on us,

12:44.200 --> 12:45.720
we won't let you down

12:45.790 --> 12:47.200
as Purong Hotel's principle is

12:47.200 --> 12:49.750
to serve our guests with sincerity

12:49.870 --> 12:51.240
and exchange sincerity for sincerity.

12:51.240 --> 12:51.790
Oh my.

12:51.910 --> 12:54.320
The students taking the exam
at Xinhua Finance and Economics School

12:54.320 --> 12:55.330
are really lucky.

12:55.470 --> 12:56.380
[Wishing everyone success
in the college entrance exam]

12:55.480 --> 12:56.500
Sold out?

12:56.400 --> 12:57.260
[Hope you can get good results]

12:56.750 --> 12:57.660
Sold out!

12:58.360 --> 12:59.420
That's wonderful.

13:01.230 --> 13:02.290
Congratulations.

13:03.390 --> 13:03.990
Thank you.

13:05.800 --> 13:08.600
Dad, why don't you understand me at all?

13:08.850 --> 13:10.040
Have you had enough?

13:10.150 --> 13:11.340
Have I had enough?

13:11.380 --> 13:12.720
Why do you always think

13:12.720 --> 13:13.810
I'm messing around?

13:13.810 --> 13:15.760
I've been to Kuanli so many times,

13:16.350 --> 13:17.750
but no one ever told me

13:17.770 --> 13:20.040
that the Venture Capital Summit
was moved to early June.

13:20.040 --> 13:20.510
Why?

13:21.240 --> 13:22.770
The reason they dare to treat me like this

13:22.770 --> 13:23.390
is because you

13:23.390 --> 13:25.120
have never stood on my side.

13:25.610 --> 13:27.830
Bastard! You're useless,

13:27.850 --> 13:29.180
but you blame it on me.

13:29.510 --> 13:31.010
Duan Aoxiang, listen!

13:31.360 --> 13:33.540
Kuanli Group is not your playground.

13:33.840 --> 13:35.600
Doing business is not playing a game.

13:35.600 --> 13:37.730
No one can
achieve a stunning success.

13:38.030 --> 13:39.900
You have a good hand.

13:40.360 --> 13:42.600
Give it to me
if you don't know how to play.

13:42.600 --> 13:44.440
I have plenty of talents.

13:58.600 --> 13:59.200
Who is it?

14:16.180 --> 14:18.580
Only an attendant
came up with me just now.

14:19.040 --> 14:20.300
I let her go down first.

14:20.630 --> 14:22.290
No one else heard it except me.

14:24.160 --> 14:26.180
Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.

14:26.960 --> 14:27.660
Come in.

15:06.150 --> 15:08.410
I'll have an attendant come and clean up.

15:13.720 --> 15:14.510
Thanks.

15:33.890 --> 15:35.610
[Li Qiaoqi]

15:34.320 --> 15:36.030
Miyu, you were amazing.

15:36.030 --> 15:37.290
I'm so happy for you.

15:37.600 --> 15:39.300
[Yin Xiang]

15:37.870 --> 15:39.860
Miyu, you were so beautiful
in the live stream.

15:39.860 --> 15:40.930
Thank you.

15:41.050 --> 15:41.890
[Xu Miyu]

15:43.890 --> 15:45.510
[Lu Xiaoyan]

15:44.460 --> 15:46.160
You are great, Ms. Xu.

15:47.570 --> 15:48.360
Thank you.

15:47.760 --> 15:48.640
[Xu Miyu]

15:48.990 --> 15:51.440
[Dianjiangchun Studio]

15:51.460 --> 15:53.250
[Light up life and spread the beauty]

15:53.350 --> 15:55.910
[Ji Feng]

16:00.150 --> 16:01.200
Mr. Ji.

16:02.770 --> 16:04.260
Why are you here?

16:05.240 --> 16:08.500
I'm here to welcome
the great contributor to Purong Hotel.

16:09.750 --> 16:10.390
By the way,

16:10.440 --> 16:12.890
I didn't have time
to ask for instructions.

16:12.910 --> 16:14.210
I just acted on my own.

16:14.390 --> 16:15.650
You did a very good job.

16:25.630 --> 16:27.000
Are you free later?

16:27.510 --> 16:28.770
I booked a restaurant.

16:29.250 --> 16:30.910
I have something to say to you.

16:32.870 --> 16:33.630
What is it?

16:35.360 --> 16:35.960
Ms. Xu.

16:37.280 --> 16:38.570
[ROSE GARDEN]

16:40.240 --> 16:40.950
Ms. Xu.

16:41.120 --> 16:43.130
I just told Hailin to keep you here.

16:43.200 --> 16:45.150
I didn't expect you to leave so quickly.

16:45.150 --> 16:46.090
Congratulations.

16:46.090 --> 16:47.510
You made a great contribution to Purong.

16:47.510 --> 16:49.960
I should thank you for
cooperating with me.

16:49.980 --> 16:52.880
Otherwise, we wouldn't have
gotten such a good result.

16:52.880 --> 16:54.720
Do you want to go for a drink later?

16:54.720 --> 16:56.250
Consider it a celebration.

16:59.210 --> 17:00.010
How about you?

17:00.280 --> 17:01.700
As Purong's representative,

17:01.700 --> 17:03.100
do you want to come along?

17:03.600 --> 17:06.329
I almost forgot. Thank you so much today.

17:06.829 --> 17:08.020
Thank you for your help.

17:08.020 --> 17:09.640
Don't change the subject on purpose.

17:09.640 --> 17:10.359
Are you coming or not?

17:10.359 --> 17:12.800
We can talk at the dinner table.

17:15.720 --> 17:17.240
It wasn't easy to organize this.

17:17.240 --> 17:19.000
You wouldn't reject me, would you?

17:19.000 --> 17:19.960
Of course not.

17:20.780 --> 17:23.079
Then, thank you, Ms. Jiang.

17:24.240 --> 17:24.770
Right.

17:25.109 --> 17:25.910
How about you?

17:25.920 --> 17:27.680
Zhichun, we have to go.

17:29.240 --> 17:30.790
Then I'll drive.

17:31.110 --> 17:31.950
Take my car.

17:32.150 --> 17:34.640
You can call a designated driver
to drive your car back later.

17:34.640 --> 17:36.500
Let's go. I'll book a restaurant.

18:24.580 --> 18:26.890
[Xu Miyu]

18:28.960 --> 18:31.160
Let's leave together when this is over.

18:41.460 --> 18:42.310
[Xu Miyu]

19:13.880 --> 19:14.880
This way, please.

19:20.100 --> 19:20.910
Thank you.

19:31.620 --> 19:32.250
Thank you.

19:36.260 --> 19:37.790
Ladies, here are the menus.

19:37.900 --> 19:38.600
Thank you.

19:43.700 --> 19:45.740
Ms. Xu, do you
have any dietary restrictions?

19:45.740 --> 19:47.070
I'm fine with anything.

19:49.290 --> 19:50.760
Their beef tartare is quite good.

19:50.760 --> 19:51.800
Why don't we try it?

19:51.800 --> 19:52.340
Sure.

19:53.750 --> 19:55.880
What other appetizers would you like?

19:55.910 --> 19:57.840
I'd like to try the Farmhouse Soup.

19:57.920 --> 20:00.720
All right. We'll have three bowls of
Farmhouse Soup.

20:00.720 --> 20:02.650
And a Chicken with Hangzhou Chili.

20:04.470 --> 20:05.090
And you?

20:07.070 --> 20:09.000
Tomato and shredded pork noodles.

20:09.290 --> 20:10.630
You still dislike

20:10.830 --> 20:12.160
their cream spaghetti?

20:19.550 --> 20:21.810
Ms. Xu, what else would you like to order?

20:25.410 --> 20:26.960
One Caesar Salad, please.

20:27.240 --> 20:29.960
I remember there is mustard
in Caesar Salad, right?

20:29.960 --> 20:30.470
Yes.

20:30.640 --> 20:31.770
Sorry, Ms. Xu.

20:31.870 --> 20:33.510
Ji Feng is allergic to mustard.

20:33.510 --> 20:34.890
Should we change another one?

20:34.890 --> 20:35.950
It doesn't matter.

20:36.030 --> 20:36.850
Let us take this.

20:36.850 --> 20:38.450
We'll have one Caesar Salad.

20:38.850 --> 20:40.250
I can eat a little bit now.

20:44.180 --> 20:45.840
What else do you want to order?

20:46.290 --> 20:47.230
Enough for me.

20:47.880 --> 20:48.270
Okay.

20:51.310 --> 20:52.110
That's all for now.

20:52.110 --> 20:52.440
Okay.

20:53.880 --> 20:54.350
Enjoy your meal.

20:54.350 --> 20:55.280
Okay. Thank you.

21:01.650 --> 21:03.610
Cherish your free time.

21:04.610 --> 21:06.340
Since you won the battle today,

21:06.340 --> 21:08.400
you'll be busy in the following days.

21:09.590 --> 21:12.100
The real preparation work
will begin the day after tomorrow.

21:12.100 --> 21:13.100
At that time,

21:13.130 --> 21:15.780
we welcome you to shoot and
collect more video materials.

21:15.780 --> 21:16.510
Don't worry.

21:16.790 --> 21:17.920
For this promotion,

21:18.200 --> 21:20.160
I'll follow up on the whole process.

21:20.160 --> 21:20.760
Thank you.

21:30.440 --> 21:31.810
Would you like desserts?

21:31.810 --> 21:32.870
No need, thank you.

21:35.980 --> 21:38.130
I know girls can't resist desserts.

21:38.510 --> 21:40.200
but their dessert tastes so-so.

21:40.200 --> 21:42.310
I know a place nearby that
I ordered from before.

21:42.310 --> 21:44.270
After we buy what we want online

21:44.560 --> 21:46.730
we can let Ji Feng pick it up.

21:47.680 --> 21:48.240
Ms. Xu,

21:49.060 --> 21:51.260
see if there's anything you want to eat.

21:51.310 --> 21:52.270
[Sesame Crisp Biscuit] [Kai Kou Xiao]

21:53.130 --> 21:54.780
Then, thank you, Mr. Ji,

21:54.830 --> 21:55.910
for making a trip for us.

21:55.910 --> 21:56.570
No problem.

22:02.320 --> 22:03.980
I'll send you the screenshot.

22:04.030 --> 22:05.490
They serve food very fast.

22:05.500 --> 22:06.350
Go ahead.

22:07.120 --> 22:07.660
Okay.

22:26.110 --> 22:28.520
Ms. Jiang knows this restaurant very well.

22:28.640 --> 22:30.140
It's not your first time here, is it?

22:30.140 --> 22:31.200
You saw through it.

22:32.470 --> 22:34.930
You are very familiar with
everything here.

22:36.400 --> 22:38.260
I've been here many times before.

22:39.200 --> 22:39.940
Do you know

22:40.510 --> 22:42.440
when the first time I came here was?

22:44.200 --> 22:46.960
It was when I won the best debater
for the first time

22:46.960 --> 22:48.960
in a debate competition in college.

22:49.320 --> 22:51.590
At that time,
Ji Feng didn't have much money.

22:51.590 --> 22:53.620
He used his first internship salary

22:53.730 --> 22:55.390
to bring me here to celebrate.

22:56.240 --> 22:59.070
Congratulations to Miss Jiang Zhichun
for winning the best debater.

22:59.070 --> 23:00.640
And congratulations to you for

23:00.640 --> 23:02.510
getting your first salary in life.

23:02.510 --> 23:02.970
Cheers.

23:06.110 --> 23:08.800
I've started
getting the hang of it lately.

23:09.400 --> 23:11.280
If everything goes well,

23:11.510 --> 23:15.110
I can become a full-time employee
after a few more job rotations.

23:21.830 --> 23:22.560
Tastes good.

23:22.890 --> 23:24.950
The dishes just now
also tasted good.

23:25.030 --> 23:27.110
Let's come to this place often, okay?

23:29.790 --> 23:30.430
Sure.

23:33.200 --> 23:35.000
My boyfriend, you are excellent.

23:35.000 --> 23:36.710
I think you'll definitely
become a full-time employee.

23:36.710 --> 23:38.300
If you perform well,

23:38.400 --> 23:41.060
you might even be promoted
straight to manager.

23:42.790 --> 23:44.270
I'll try my best.

23:56.720 --> 23:57.520
What's wrong?

23:58.880 --> 23:59.540
Too greasy.

24:00.160 --> 24:01.640
Really? Let me taste it.

24:11.720 --> 24:13.850
I think it's pretty good.

24:13.960 --> 24:15.680
Then, I'll order it for you next time.

24:15.680 --> 24:16.480
I dislike it.

24:21.680 --> 24:22.350
Come on.

24:22.920 --> 24:23.920
Drink some water.

24:28.270 --> 24:29.610
At that time, I thought

24:29.920 --> 24:31.400
I was so lucky.

24:32.110 --> 24:33.350
At the right time,

24:34.200 --> 24:36.200
I was staying with the right person.

24:36.480 --> 24:38.510
Even the randomly chosen restaurant

24:38.510 --> 24:39.640
was so perfect.

24:40.160 --> 24:41.690
Everything was just right.

24:42.960 --> 24:44.890
I didn't expect this restaurant to

24:44.960 --> 24:46.760
have been open for over a decade.

24:47.480 --> 24:48.610
Actually, later on,

24:48.680 --> 24:50.480
I came here by myself a few times.

24:51.440 --> 24:53.500
Maybe because my mood was different,

24:53.680 --> 24:56.080
the dishes didn't taste the same
as before.

24:56.420 --> 24:58.750
Actually, there's no such thing as
"just right."

24:58.750 --> 24:59.810
All the perfection

25:00.750 --> 25:02.480
was just him accommodating me.

25:03.440 --> 25:06.590
He is great. But I didn't cherish him.

25:07.160 --> 25:08.690
So I regret it very much now.

25:08.830 --> 25:11.030
I really want to mend our relationship.

25:11.260 --> 25:13.120
Do you think it's still possible?

25:24.160 --> 25:24.880
Ms. Xu.

25:25.830 --> 25:27.360
Do you feel disillusioned?

25:27.960 --> 25:30.860
A blogger who has always
flaunted being an independent woman

25:30.860 --> 25:32.550
unexpectedly, in real life,

25:33.000 --> 25:34.660
is so hesitant and conflicted

25:34.920 --> 25:36.770
when it comes to relationships.

25:36.920 --> 25:37.480
No.

25:38.960 --> 25:41.090
Thank you for your honesty, Ms. Jiang.

25:42.920 --> 25:44.100
But I think

25:44.750 --> 25:46.550
the choice of your relationship is

25:46.550 --> 25:48.030
in the hands of you two.

25:49.110 --> 25:51.430
I don't know much about your past,

25:52.110 --> 25:54.170
and I won't interfere in your future.

25:54.330 --> 25:55.930
If you have something to say,

25:57.440 --> 25:59.770
I think you'd better tell Mr. Ji directly.

26:11.990 --> 26:12.720
Here you are.

26:12.960 --> 26:13.560
Thank you.

26:14.110 --> 26:14.910
Where is Miyu?

26:15.680 --> 26:17.030
Ms. Xu said there's something
at the hotel,

26:17.030 --> 26:18.630
so she went back to handle it.

26:19.590 --> 26:20.650
Did she just leave?

26:24.240 --> 26:25.070
Ji Feng!

26:37.350 --> 26:37.880
Miyu!

26:43.310 --> 26:44.370
I'll take you back.

26:44.640 --> 26:46.500
No need. I've booked a rideshare.

26:46.720 --> 26:47.920
The car is already here.

26:47.920 --> 26:49.650
The pickup point is right here.

26:50.340 --> 26:52.580
Did she say something to you?

26:53.680 --> 26:54.350
No.

26:54.400 --> 26:56.110
There is something in the hotel.

26:56.110 --> 26:57.030
I need to go back and handle it.

26:57.030 --> 26:58.430
I'll leave it to you guys.

26:58.500 --> 27:00.850
Miyu, I have something to tell you.

27:00.960 --> 27:02.290
Let's talk another day.

27:03.550 --> 27:04.480
I'm tired today.

27:22.980 --> 27:24.490
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

27:26.490 --> 27:28.150
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

27:30.350 --> 27:32.260
♪ People in the city ♪

27:33.080 --> 27:36.020
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

27:34.100 --> 27:35.830
Actually, I know very well that

27:36.750 --> 27:38.410
things turning out like this

27:37.950 --> 27:39.760
♪ The palms of time ♪

27:38.440 --> 27:39.700
isn't anyone's fault.

27:40.240 --> 27:42.170
It's just that a relationship
among three people is too complicated.

27:41.660 --> 27:44.800
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

27:43.110 --> 27:44.750
Those back-and-forth confrontations

27:44.750 --> 27:46.440
have drained too much of my energy.

27:45.410 --> 27:47.750
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

27:47.510 --> 27:49.960
Maybe it's not that hard to
cheer up and face it.

27:49.330 --> 27:51.430
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

27:50.830 --> 27:51.750
But right now,

27:52.510 --> 27:54.760
do I really need a relationship like this?

27:52.800 --> 27:56.130
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

27:56.640 --> 27:59.670
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

28:00.260 --> 28:03.380
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

28:04.110 --> 28:06.350
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

28:08.160 --> 28:11.350
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

28:12.020 --> 28:15.390
♪ The forgotten past ♪

28:16.370 --> 28:18.640
♪ There may be regrets ♪

28:20.300 --> 28:22.540
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

28:30.880 --> 28:32.740
The stationery delivery is here.

28:43.930 --> 28:44.790
Just put it here.

28:44.790 --> 28:45.510
Over here.

28:58.720 --> 28:59.240
Come on.

28:59.550 --> 29:00.790
Let's pack up the stationery sets.

29:00.790 --> 29:01.750
Each requires three pencils,

29:01.750 --> 29:02.920
one eraser,

29:03.160 --> 29:04.110
one pencil sharpener,

29:04.110 --> 29:05.400
two pens,

29:05.480 --> 29:06.400
one notebook,

29:06.400 --> 29:07.550
plus a box of binder clips.

29:07.550 --> 29:08.640
We have to prepare 600 sets in total.

29:08.640 --> 29:09.480
Let's do it.

29:09.480 --> 29:10.070
Okay.

29:14.320 --> 29:15.720
Tell me when you're done.

29:28.640 --> 29:29.490
Ms. He,

29:29.830 --> 29:31.570
the writing desks and
stationery for exam-takers

29:31.570 --> 29:32.900
have all been prepared.

29:32.960 --> 29:33.400
Okay.

29:33.790 --> 29:35.000
Ms. Xu instructed us

29:35.000 --> 29:37.240
to remember to
test the internet speed at noon.

29:37.240 --> 29:37.870
Okay.

29:43.120 --> 29:47.320
[Purong Hotel]

29:44.590 --> 29:45.240
Morning.

29:45.880 --> 29:47.140
Hello, Ms. Xu.

29:48.390 --> 29:50.350
Everyone will have to work hard today.

29:50.350 --> 29:51.400
Guests will come here

29:51.400 --> 29:52.860
one after another to check in shortly.

29:52.860 --> 29:54.200
Remember to carefully check

29:54.200 --> 29:55.560
exam-takers' admission tickets.

29:55.560 --> 29:56.200
In addition,

29:56.200 --> 29:58.580
report any guests
with special needs immediately.

29:58.580 --> 29:59.700
We must meet the guests' needs

29:59.700 --> 30:00.920
as quickly as possible.

30:00.920 --> 30:01.400
Yes.

30:07.350 --> 30:08.630
Welcome.

30:20.310 --> 30:21.920
Here are our ID cards

30:22.170 --> 30:23.130
and the child's admission ticket.

30:23.130 --> 30:24.660
Okay, please wait a moment.

30:26.860 --> 30:28.130
Stop looking at your phone.

30:28.130 --> 30:30.060
Pay the bill with your credit card.

30:33.790 --> 30:34.740
Here is your bill.

30:34.740 --> 30:36.090
Please sign it.

30:40.110 --> 30:41.320
Why is this price?

30:41.350 --> 30:43.590
Didn't we agree on a half-price discount?

30:43.590 --> 30:44.430
It is half price,

30:44.430 --> 30:45.880
but you booked the executive floor.

30:45.880 --> 30:48.830
This is the price for a room
on the executive floor after the discount.

30:48.830 --> 30:50.000
You booked the executive floor?

30:50.000 --> 30:51.470
Our child's college entrance exam is

30:51.470 --> 30:52.750
the most important thing.

30:52.750 --> 30:54.240
Of course,
we have to stay in the best room.

30:54.240 --> 30:56.090
This is a five-star hotel.

30:56.680 --> 30:59.370
The accommodation and food are fine.

30:59.550 --> 31:01.840
Why did you book an executive suite?

31:03.030 --> 31:05.120
Why can't we book an executive suite?

31:05.480 --> 31:07.140
You don't usually save money.

31:07.480 --> 31:08.640
Our kid is
taking the college entrance exam.

31:08.640 --> 31:09.920
For such a big deal,

31:10.030 --> 31:11.720
you're being stingy?

31:11.790 --> 31:13.320
What kind of father are you?

31:13.590 --> 31:15.520
I just don't think it's necessary.

31:16.100 --> 31:17.980
Why isn't it necessary?

31:18.030 --> 31:20.610
You snore so loudly at night.

31:20.630 --> 31:21.960
If I don't get a suite,

31:21.960 --> 31:23.640
what if our child can't sleep well?

31:23.640 --> 31:25.900
Then, you shouldn't have let my dad come.

31:25.910 --> 31:27.740
Liu Yuze, just be quiet.

31:28.030 --> 31:29.240
Sorry to interrupt.

31:29.310 --> 31:30.410
How about this?

31:30.480 --> 31:31.830
Please follow me to the executive floor

31:31.830 --> 31:32.950
to check in.

31:32.980 --> 31:34.240
Come, this way please.

31:35.320 --> 31:36.740
Hurry up.

31:37.200 --> 31:39.110
Hurry up and go to your room
so you can start studying.

31:39.110 --> 31:40.310
I got you such a nice room,

31:40.310 --> 31:41.640
but you're ungrateful.

31:43.240 --> 31:44.380
Welcome.

31:44.440 --> 31:45.440
This way, please.

31:47.480 --> 31:48.270
Ms. Xu.

31:48.400 --> 31:49.440
The network signal for
the rooms on the east side

31:49.440 --> 31:50.720
has already been tested.

31:50.720 --> 31:52.050
Guests can check in now.

31:52.110 --> 31:54.260
The workers of the Engineering Department
are testing the west side.

31:54.260 --> 31:55.440
It should be done soon.

31:55.440 --> 31:56.920
Okay, I'll leave this to you.

31:56.920 --> 31:58.920
By the way,
this student has some hearing problems.

31:58.920 --> 32:00.030
Please take extra care of him.

32:00.030 --> 32:01.480
Don't worry, leave it to me.

32:01.480 --> 32:02.070
Ms. Xu,

32:02.160 --> 32:03.400
a guest in the lobby said

32:03.400 --> 32:05.030
they didn't get the livestream booking

32:05.030 --> 32:06.790
but booked an exam-taker room
through the platform.

32:06.790 --> 32:08.660
They want to know whether
they can enjoy the discount.

32:08.660 --> 32:10.390
Copy that. I'm coming down now.

32:10.680 --> 32:11.510
I'll go then.

32:11.590 --> 32:12.520
Get back to work.

32:17.720 --> 32:20.350
The discount for exam-taker rooms
on the platform

32:20.350 --> 32:22.770
and those booked through
Dianjiangchun's stream is the same.

32:22.770 --> 32:24.990
What about the stream's half-hour voucher?

32:24.990 --> 32:26.010
That takes off 20 yuan.

32:26.010 --> 32:27.420
This is an exclusive discount of
the live-streaming room.

32:27.420 --> 32:29.830
Purong can't provide
you with this discount.

32:29.830 --> 32:30.690
How about this?

32:30.740 --> 32:31.990
After you check in,

32:32.020 --> 32:35.000
we'll give you a voucher for
the hotel's Chinese restaurant

32:35.000 --> 32:36.030
as a token of our appreciation.

32:36.030 --> 32:37.240
Does it work for you?

32:37.240 --> 32:38.130
Okay.

32:38.310 --> 32:40.030
Remember to send it to our room later.

32:40.030 --> 32:40.550
Okay, no problem.

32:40.550 --> 32:41.590
Come on, I'll arrange it.

32:41.590 --> 32:42.590
This way, please.

32:49.030 --> 32:50.310
Give this guest

32:50.310 --> 32:51.240
a 30-yuan voucher.

32:51.240 --> 32:52.240
Okay, no problem.

33:12.110 --> 33:13.600
Be quick.

33:14.000 --> 33:15.350
Watch the heat here.

33:16.290 --> 33:18.100
Don't put too much oil, okay?

33:19.990 --> 33:21.380
How long will it take to be ready?

33:21.380 --> 33:22.200
Ten minutes.

33:22.550 --> 33:23.350
Guo?

33:23.890 --> 33:24.520
I'm here.

33:24.550 --> 33:26.180
Get as much of that as you have, hurry up.

33:26.180 --> 33:26.660
Okay.

33:27.020 --> 33:28.240
We still need two people here.

33:28.240 --> 33:29.940
Let someone come here quickly.

33:29.940 --> 33:30.800
Ya?

33:31.480 --> 33:32.280
-Qiaoqi.
-Ya.

33:33.330 --> 33:34.490
It's today's set meal.

33:34.490 --> 33:35.600
Where's the Yan Du Xian?

33:35.600 --> 33:37.060
Here comes the Yan Du Xian.

33:38.510 --> 33:39.460
Serve it just like this.

33:39.460 --> 33:40.220
Okay.

33:46.310 --> 33:48.050
Please enjoy today's set meal.

33:50.480 --> 33:51.830
Braised pork ribs. I like it.

33:51.830 --> 33:53.890
We'll have a cold appetizer platter,

33:54.030 --> 33:55.630
pork potstickers,

33:55.830 --> 33:58.230
scallion oil noodles and mung bean soup.

33:58.250 --> 33:58.910
Okay.

33:59.590 --> 34:00.480
Try it.

34:01.550 --> 34:03.220
We'd like a portion of that set meal too.

34:03.220 --> 34:04.680
It looks quite delicious.

34:04.720 --> 34:05.480
All right.

34:10.280 --> 34:11.360
Hello, distinguished guests.

34:11.360 --> 34:12.340
Kind reminder from Purong Hotel:

34:12.340 --> 34:13.500
it's morning now.

34:13.710 --> 34:15.110
The buffet restaurant opens at 6:30.

34:15.110 --> 34:17.110
You can come to have your breakfast.

34:22.110 --> 34:24.170
The buffet restaurant opens at 6:30.

34:36.590 --> 34:38.650
If the buffet restaurant is

34:38.670 --> 34:39.600
short of people,

34:39.639 --> 34:41.400
you can go help out.

34:41.400 --> 34:43.750
I often help serve dishes.

34:44.480 --> 34:45.070
Zhichun.

34:47.070 --> 34:47.760
Then, you can go back to work.

34:47.760 --> 34:48.360
Okay.

34:50.550 --> 34:52.550
Why are you here?

34:52.570 --> 34:54.030
I'm here to shoot some footage.

34:54.030 --> 34:55.560
Did you get what you needed?

34:55.889 --> 34:56.750
I got a lot.

34:57.150 --> 34:57.510
Okay.

34:58.360 --> 34:59.800
Take your time shooting.

34:59.800 --> 35:00.740
I'll be leaving.

35:00.820 --> 35:02.680
Find Xue Rui if you need anything.

35:09.000 --> 35:09.920
Let's rest for a while

35:09.920 --> 35:12.050
and shoot when exam-takers come back.

35:14.350 --> 35:15.360
They are back.

35:29.330 --> 35:30.530
Everyone, get ready.

35:30.950 --> 35:31.630
Come on.

35:32.630 --> 35:33.360
Go. Go. Go.

36:02.370 --> 36:04.400
Come, serve the food.

36:04.620 --> 36:05.410
Come on. Here

36:10.950 --> 36:11.990
Come help.

36:13.440 --> 36:14.120
Go.

36:14.600 --> 36:15.460
Serve the food.

37:42.350 --> 37:46.360
[Xu Miyu]

38:03.550 --> 38:05.480
During the college entrance exam,

38:06.080 --> 38:08.010
Mr. Ji, you don't have other plans?

38:09.400 --> 38:10.530
I'm busy.

38:11.190 --> 38:13.060
Meiqi, two Americanos, please.

38:13.320 --> 38:13.800
Okay.

38:16.150 --> 38:16.780
What about you?

38:16.780 --> 38:18.040
What are you busy with?

38:18.590 --> 38:20.110
I thought I'd be very busy,

38:21.150 --> 38:22.350
but I overthought it.

38:25.710 --> 38:27.190
Mr. Ji, your Americanos.

38:37.360 --> 38:38.620
Actually, sometimes,

38:40.190 --> 38:41.320
I really envy you.

38:42.110 --> 38:44.750
The heir of Kuanli Group envies me?

38:47.120 --> 38:50.030
Don't think
I can't tell that you're being sarcastic.

38:50.030 --> 38:51.480
I didn't mean that at all.

38:53.230 --> 38:54.360
I just think

38:55.510 --> 38:57.240
it would be great to be like you,

38:57.260 --> 38:59.120
who can do whatever you want to do.

39:02.000 --> 39:04.750
The feeling of fighting for
something for yourself

39:04.750 --> 39:06.280
must be really good, right?

39:08.480 --> 39:09.940
What are you trying to say?

39:14.230 --> 39:16.110
Honestly, I don't know what I want to say.

39:16.110 --> 39:17.880
Ever since I was born,

39:18.030 --> 39:20.360
I've been doing
what my dad wanted me to do.

39:21.480 --> 39:23.800
He asks for so much.

39:24.550 --> 39:25.880
I can never satisfy him.

39:27.110 --> 39:28.510
I look like a loser.

39:29.870 --> 39:30.400
Mr. Duan.

39:31.360 --> 39:33.040
If you give up so early,

39:33.190 --> 39:35.360
I'll think that in terms of
our VAM agreement,

39:35.360 --> 39:36.420
I have already won.

39:38.770 --> 39:39.770
How could that be?

40:08.950 --> 40:11.210
Our hotel has never been so empty.

40:12.550 --> 40:13.650
Only for now.

40:13.680 --> 40:14.630
At noon,

40:14.630 --> 40:16.880
they all rushed back to eat and sleep.

40:16.960 --> 40:18.460
It was packed with people over there.

40:18.460 --> 40:19.670
So scary.

40:21.550 --> 40:22.430
Xiaoyan,

40:22.670 --> 40:25.270
how did your cousin do
on his exam this morning?

40:26.030 --> 40:26.920
I don't know.

40:26.920 --> 40:28.480
He didn't say anything when I asked him.

40:28.480 --> 40:30.560
He used his phone all noon,

40:30.630 --> 40:32.830
checking answers with his classmates.

40:34.880 --> 40:35.480
Looks like they're back.

40:35.480 --> 40:36.280
They are back.

40:41.370 --> 40:42.770
HSKP Department. HSKP Department.

40:42.770 --> 40:44.110
Finish the turndown service
as soon as possible.

40:44.110 --> 40:45.000
The guests are back.

40:45.000 --> 40:47.130
Ready? If so, send them out right away.

40:47.220 --> 40:49.140
Is tonight's supper menu ready?

40:49.710 --> 40:50.370
Right here.

40:51.150 --> 40:52.190
You can take a look,
I'll deal with something.

40:52.190 --> 40:52.550
Okay.

40:55.000 --> 40:56.240
Ms. Xu. Ms. Xu.

40:57.280 --> 41:00.080
A guest at the front desk is
complaining about a lost valuable.

41:00.080 --> 41:01.610
Got it, I'll be right there.

41:04.080 --> 41:06.270
My son's hearing aid was customized.

41:06.700 --> 41:08.470
You just said you hadn't found it.
That is it?

41:08.470 --> 41:09.590
What am I supposed to do?

41:09.590 --> 41:10.670
What about
tomorrow's English listening exam?

41:10.670 --> 41:11.550
What is my son going to do?

41:11.550 --> 41:13.070
Ma'am, please calm down.

41:13.090 --> 41:14.670
What is the point of giving me water?

41:14.670 --> 41:16.780
What I want is my son's hearing aid.

41:17.110 --> 41:18.840
Ma'am, please calm down first.

41:19.080 --> 41:20.600
I'll help you solve
whatever the problem is.
